ed</item></change><change n="meta.33734"><date>2009-03-21</date><respStmt><name>IDP</name></respStmt><item>Crosswalked to EpiDoc XML</item></change></revisionDesc></teiHeader><text><body><head lang="en"><date>IVspc</date>
<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Oxyrhynchus</placeName></head><div type="edition" lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">κυρίῳ μου υἱῷ</supplied> <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">Θ</unclear>εοδότῳ 

    <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">Δί</supplied>δυμος. 

    <lb n="3"/><gap reason="illegible" extent="2" unit="character"/><gap reason="lost" extent="2" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/><gap reason="lost" extent="1" unit="character"/> <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">Ἀ</unclear>σίων <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">τ</unclear>ὴν τύχην 

    <lb n="4"/>ἑαυτοῦ ἐχλεύασεν καὶ οὐχὶ 

    <lb n="5"/>τὴν ἐμὴν ἐάσας τὸ χωρίον 

    <lb n="6"/>εἰς ἔρημον· <choice><corr>ἀρκεσθεὶ<supplied reason="omitted" cert="high">ς</supplied></corr><sic>αρκεσθει</sic></choice> γὰρ ὑπὲρ 

    <lb n="7"/>τῆς γυναικὸς <choice><corr>δείκνυ</corr><sic>διγνου</sic></choice> ὥστε 

    <lb n="8"/>τὰ τέκνα α<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ὐτῆς</unclear> ἐνέγκαι 

    <lb n="9"/>εἰς ἀμπελουργίαν τοῦ χωρίου. 

    <lb n="10"/>εἰδὼς οὖν ὅτι <choice><corr>χρεία</corr><sic>χρια</sic></choice> μού 

    <lb n="11"/>ἐστιν ἐπὶ τῆς πόλεως 

    <lb n="12"/>μάλιστα διὰ τὰ δημόσια 

    <lb n="13"/>καὶ τὰ ἄλλα, σπούδασον κα-

    <lb n="14"/>τ᾽ αὐτὴν τὴν ῥοπὴν <choice><corr>καταναγ-

    <lb n="15"/>κάσαι</corr><sic>καταναγκασε</sic></choice> Ἀσίωνα ὥστε τὴν 

    <lb n="16"/>παράστασιν τῆς γυναικὸς 

    <lb n="17"/>ποιῆσαι μετὰ καὶ τῶν τέ-

    <lb n="18"/>κνων αὐτῆς. καὶ τὸν γαμ-

    <lb n="19"/>βρὸν δὲ <choice><corr>ἀπόστειλον</corr><sic>α<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">π</unclear>οστιλον</sic></choice> ἅμα 

    <lb n="20"/>αὐτῶν πρὶν τοῦ με τὴν 

    <lb n="21"/>ὁρμὴν ποι<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ῆ</unclear>σαι ἐπὶ τὴν 

    <lb n="22"/>πόλιν <hi rend="diaeresis">ἵ</hi>να δυνηθῶ τυπῶ-

    <lb n="23"/>σαι τὸ χωρίον κατὰ λόγον 

    <lb n="24"/>πρὶν ὁδεῦσαι. μετὰ στρε-

    <lb n="25"/>βλώσεως οὖν <choice><corr>ἀπόστειλον</corr><sic>αποστιλον</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="26"/>Ἀσίωνα ἅμα αὐτῶν. 

    <lb n="27"/><handShift new="m2"/> ἐρρῶσθαί σε εὔχομαι 

    <lb n="28"/>πολλοῖς χρόν<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">οις</unclear> 

    <lb n="29"/>κύριέ μου υἱέ. 

    <lb n="30"/><handShift new="m1"/> <del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable">παράσχου <hi rend="diaeresis">Ἰ</hi>σὰκ Φανβ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">α</unclear>ρτὸν</del> 

    <lb n="31"/><del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable">εἰς <choice><corr>συμπλήρωσι<supplied reason="omitted" cert="high">ν</supplied></corr><sic>συνπληρωσει</sic></choice> </del> 

    <lb n="32,ms" rend="perpendicular"/> μετὰ στρεβλώσεως μεθόδευσον Ἑρμίαν τὰ δύο <num value="2"/> διπλᾶ Ἀθανασίου ἐπικου<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> </ab></div><div n="meta.33734" type="description" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><rs type="material" cert="high">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.33734" type="commentary" subtype="textDate" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><date type="textDate" notBefore="301" notAfter="400">IV</date></p></div><div n="meta.33734" type="bibliography" subtype="principalEdition" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="principal" default="NO"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Oxy.</title><biblScope type="volume">48</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">3430</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos" default="NO"><biblScope type="numbers">33734</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP" default="NO"><series>0181</series>; <biblScope type="volume">48</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">3430</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref type="Perseus" href="0181;48;3430" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.33734" type="bibliography" subtype="illustrations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.33734" type="history" subtype="locations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><placeName type="ancientFindspot" cert="high" full="yes">Oxyrhynchos</placeName></p></div><div n="meta.33734" type="figure" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><figure href="http://163.1.169.40/cgi-bin/library?e=d-000-00---0POxy--00-0-0-0prompt-10---4---Document---0-1l--1-en-50---20-about---001-001-1-0utfZz-8-00031-001-1-0utfZz-8-00&amp;a=d&amp;c=POxy&amp;cl=CL5.1.14&amp;d=HASH52a3265c3fa3e210c81ce4"><figDesc>Abbildung im Internet</figDesc></figure></p></div></body></text></TEI.2>